description.en:
A collection of oneshots, the main story features Yoshi Kagami from the Prince Charming series, and an appearance by hypochondriac Chihana from 35 Degrees of Love.

1) Suki ni Nattara 10 made Kazoero
A college student locked out of his apartment finds out about the sleep disorder of his salaryman neighbor.

2) Shinshi no Tashinami
The charismatic chief's beautiful bentos must be made with love. But whose?

3) Otona no Kuchibiru
Can the company president's private secretary keep his cool when the president's son needs a place to stay? Sequel to chapter 2, "Lip Service" from My Bodyguard.

4) Hana no Nai 2-gatsu no Mori
A young man inherits a house, and a garden that reminds him of his lost love.

5) Shiawase ni Narisokoneta Otoko
Little extra for the first chapter.
